ed="T" n="0803a14"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0803a14"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>京師安國寺<persName key="A011099">藏用</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0803a15"/><persName key="A011099">釋藏用</persName>，不詳何許人也。從其拔俗，依棲<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩<lb
ed="T" n="0803a16"/>山</placeName><persName key="A019379">空公</persName>為師。及乎年當應法，即於<placeName key="PL000000043791">汾川</placeName><persName key="A011100">炬<lb
ed="T" n="0803a17"/>律師</persName>所受上品形俱法。登詣<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛中</placeName><persName key="A011101">業公</persName>講<lb
ed="T" n="0803a18"/><anchor xml:id="beg0803001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>肄</sic><corr>肆</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0803001"/>，研覈律文，循其奧妙，無所不臻。洎聞<lb
ed="T" n="0803a19"/>有禪觀之學，遂登<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬</placeName>陟<placeName key="PL000000028928">霍</placeName>，涉<placeName key="PL000000026396">漢</placeName>泛<placeName key="PL000000028611">湘</placeName>，望<lb
ed="T" n="0803a20"/>雙峯之叢林。又歸，開法<placeName key="PL000000042189">京輦</placeName>，道既精粹，訓且<lb
ed="T" n="0803a21"/>均敷，藹然為物楷模，嚮風宗重。當<date notBefore-iso="+0780-02-15" key="j20059942007439" notAfter-iso="+0784-01-30">建中中</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0803a22"/>已全三十許臘。尋應詔充臨壇首席，相繼<lb
ed="T" n="0803a23"/>度弟子越多。及居東城化塔，乃<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>之邸<lb
ed="T" n="0803a24"/>第也，推<persName key="A011099">用</persName>主其綱任。苾<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz5"/>芻<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz5"/>至息慈，皆遵畏<lb
ed="T" n="0803a25"/>愛焉。席熊延客，揮麈開談，指<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡山</placeName>石也，<lb
ed="T" n="0803a26"/>有以識前身；傳<persName key="A001719">曹谿</persName>鉢也，有以知後際。是<lb
ed="T" n="0803a27"/>以門多長者之轍，室滿度人之籌，益物良<lb
ed="T" n="0803a28"/>深，坐鎮雅俗。<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28"><name>貞元</name>中</date>，左司正郎<persName key="A011103">王鋗</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000005319">南臺</placeName><persName key="A011105">崔<lb
ed="T" n="0803a29"/>公繼</persName>和之。如是數公將議標題，兵部正郎<persName key="A011106">程<pb ed="T" n="0803b" xml:id="T50.2061.0803b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0803b01"/>浩</persName>作都序，職方正郎知制誥<persName key="A011107">吳通微</persName>書之。<date from-iso="+0788-02-16" key="j20089172009270" to-iso="+0789-02-03">四<lb
ed="T" n="0803b02"/>年戊辰歲</date>也。<persName key="A011099">用</persName>公長於律學，急護任持。為<lb
ed="T" n="0803b03"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">上都</placeName>之表則也。</p>
